1. Moj brat i ja smo članovi istog *društva*. (My brother and I are members of the same *society*.)
2. Ovo *društvo* je osnovano pre pet godina. (This *company* was founded five years ago.)
3. Društvene mreže su popularna forma *društvenog* povezivanja. (Social media is a popular form of *social* networking.)
4. Moramo povećati nivo *društvene* solidarnosti. (We need to increase the level of *social* solidarity.)
5. Oni su organizovali *društveni* događaj u parku. (They organized a *social* event in the park.)
6. *Društva* su odgovorna za plaćanje poreza. (Companies are responsible for paying taxes.)
7. U našem *društvu* se cene ljudi koji su iskreni i vredni. (In our *society*, people who are honest and hardworking are valued.)
8. Ovaj problem zahteva rešenje *društvenih* struktura. (This problem requires a solution from *social* structures.)